htly ticklish</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukoshi kusuguttai you na</span></p><p begin="13.970" end="16.370" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="13.970" end="14.330">眠</span><span begin="14.330" end="14.530">気</span><span begin="14.530" end="14.660">に</span><span begin="14.660" end="15.410">誘</span><span begin="15.410" end="15.690">わ</span><span begin="15.690" end="15.900">れ</span><span begin="16.000" end="16.370">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">睡意逐渐袭来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Invited by sleepiness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemuke ni sasowarete</span></p><p begin="16.830" end="19.910" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.830" end="17.210">ま</span><span begin="17.210" end="17.520">だ</span><span begin="17.900" end="18.110">点</span><span begin="18.110" end="18.280">い</span><span begin="18.280" end="18.490">て</span><span begin="18.490" end="18.640">る</span><span begin="18.640" end="18.990">蛍</span><span begin="18.990" end="19.230">光</span><span begin="19.330" end="19.910">灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">依然亮着的荧光灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The fluorescent light still turned on</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mada tsuiteru keikoutou</span></p><p begin="20.360" end="22.770" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.360" end="20.620">フィ</span><span begin="20.620" end="20.760">ル</span><span begin="20.760" end="20.970">ム</span><span begin="20.970" end="21.080">の</span><span begin="21.080" end="21.710">白</span><span begin="21.710" end="22.100">に</span><span begin="22.200" end="22.430">な</span><span begin="22.430" end="22.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">化作胶片上的留白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turns into the white of the film</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Firumu no shiro ni naru</span></p><p begin="23.240" end="27.740" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.240" end="24.350">氷</span><span begin="24.350" end="24.540">を</span><span begin="24.540" end="25.030">口</span><span begin="25.030" end="25.290">で</span><span begin="25.390" end="25.770">砕</span><span begin="25.770" end="25.960">い</span><span begin="25.960" end="26.090">て</span><span begin="26.090" end="26.460">キ</span><span begin="26.460" end="26.800">ス</span><span begin="26.800" end="27.140">を</span><span begin="27.140" end="27.430">す</span><span begin="27.430" end="27.740">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在口中咬碎冰块然后亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crushing ice in the mouth and kissing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koori o kuchi de kudaite kisu o suru</span></p><p begin="28.250" end="31.360" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.250" end="28.640">あ</span><span begin="28.640" end="28.850">あ</span><span begin="29.310" end="29.710">冷</span><span begin="29.710" end="29.910">た</span><span begin="29.910" end="30.080">い</span><span begin="30.080" end="30.420">息</span><span begin="30.420" end="30.740">を</span><span begin="30.740" end="30.990">吐</span><span begin="30.990" end="31.360">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊 呼出冰冷的气息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah breathing out a cold breath</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa tsumetai iki o haku</span></p><p begin="31.800" end="35.420" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.800" end="32.170">二</span><span begin="32.170" end="32.390">人</span><span begin="32.390" end="32.560">は</span><span begin="32.560" end="32.750">も</span><span begin="32.750" end="33.110">う</span><span begin="33.110" end="33.860">夢</span><span begin="33.860" end="34.340">の</span><span begin="34.340" end="35.420">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">两人已然身处梦中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The two of us are already inside a dream</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futari wa mou yume no naka</span></p><p begin="57.920" end="1:01.110" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.920" end="58.270">冷</span><span begin="58.270" end="58.890">房</span><span begin="58.990" end="59.220">消</span><span begin="59.220" end="59.560">し</span><span begin="59.560" end="59.880">て</span><span begin="59.880" end="1:00.740">君</span><span begin="1:00.740" end="1:01.110">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">关掉冷气 你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turning off the AC you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Reibou keshite kimi wa</span></p><p begin="1:01.690" end="1:06.810" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.690" end="1:02.100">窓</span><span begin="1:02.100" end="1:02.430">辺</span><span begin="1:02.430" end="1:02.790">に</span><span begin="1:02.790" end="1:03.120">も</span><span begin="1:03.120" end="1:03.620">た</span><span begin="1:03.620" end="1:03.970">れ</span><span begin="1:04.640" end="1:05.310">風</span><span begin="1:05.310" end="1:05.600">に</span><span begin="1:05.600" end="1:05.780">揺</span><span begin="1:05.780" end="1:05.980">ら</span><span begin="1:05.980" end="1:06.470">れ</span><span begin="1:06.470" end="1:06.810">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">靠在窗边随风摇曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Lean by the window swayed by the wind</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Madobe ni motare kaze ni yurareru</span></p><p begin="1:07.160" end="1:09.130" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.160" end="1:07.770">夏</span><span begin="1:07.770" end="1:08.250">の</span><span begin="1:08.250" end="1:09.130">夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夏日之夜</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Summer night</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Natsu no yoru</span></p><p begin="1:10.220" end="1:14.580" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.220" end="1:10.620">花</span><span begin="1:10.620" end="1:10.770">火</span><span begin="1:10.770" end="1:10.960">は</span><span begin="1:10.960" end="1:11.300">今</span><span begin="1:11.300" end="1:11.870">年</span><span begin="1:11.870" end="1:12.290">も</span><span begin="1:12.430" end="1:12.890">見</span><span begin="1:12.890" end="1:13.260">れ</span><span begin="1:13.260" end="1:13.820">な</span><span begin="1:13.820" end="1:14.220">い</span><span begin="1:14.330" end="1:14.580">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">今年也看不了烟花了呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We can&apos;t see the fireworks this year either huh</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hanabi wa kotoshi mo mirenai ne</span></p><p begin="1:15.770" end="1:20.270" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.770" end="1:15.990">不</span><span begin="1:15.990" end="1:16.480">満</span><span begin="1:16.480" end="1:16.720">げ</span><span begin="1:16.720" end="1:17.210">に</span><span begin="1:18.620" end="1:19.340">頷</span><span begin="1:19.340" end="1:19.540">い</span><span begin="1:19.540" end="1:19.780">た</span><span begin="1:19.900" end="1:20.270">君</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">面露不满地点了点头的你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You nodded looking dissatisfied</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fumange ni unazuita kimi</span></p><p begin="1:20.750" end="1:23.250" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.750" end="1:21.110">重</span><span begin="1:21.110" end="1:21.300">た</span><span begin="1:21.300" end="1:21.450">い</span><span begin="1:21.800" end="1:22.400">瞼</span><span begin="1:22.400" end="1:22.580">を</span><span begin="1:22.770" end="1:23.130">擦</span><span begin="1:23.130" end="1:23.250">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">揉着沉重的眼睑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Rubbing heavy eyelids</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omotai mabuta o kosuru</span></p><p begin="1:23.600" end="1:26.190" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.600" end="1:24.190">煙草</span><span begin="1:24.190" end="1:24.360">の</span><span begin="1:24.680" end="1:25.260">煙</span><span begin="1:25.260" end="1:25.450">が</span><span begin="1:25.590" end="1:25.770">染</span><span begin="1:25.770" end="1:25.970">み</span><span begin="1:25.970" end="1:26.190">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">香烟的烟雾有些刺眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The cigarette smoke stings</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tabako no kemuri ga shimiru</span></p><p begin="1:26.490" end="1:31.780" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.490" end="1:27.070">私</span><span begin="1:27.070" end="1:27.200">の</span><span begin="1:27.540" end="1:28.120">隣</span><span begin="1:28.120" end="1:28.320">で</span><span begin="1:28.440" end="1:28.800">少</span><span begin="1:28.800" end="1:28.970">し</span><span begin="1:28.970" end="1:29.540">窮</span><span begin="1:29.540" end="1:30.050">屈</span><span begin="1:30.050" end="1:30.320">そ</span><span begin="1:30.320" end="1:30.660">う</span><span begin="1:30.660" end="1:30.970">に</span><span begin="1:30.970" end="1:31.500">笑</span><span begin="1:31.500" end="1:31.780">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我身旁略显局促地笑着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Smiling looking a little cramped next to me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no tonari de sukoshi kyuukutsusou ni warau</span></p><p begin="1:32.170" end="1:34.740" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.170" end="1:32.520">甘</span><span begin="1:32.520" end="1:32.780">さ</span><span begin="1:32.780" end="1:32.870">の</span><span begin="1:33.150" end="1:33.450">控</span><span begin="1:33.450" end="1:33.650">え</span><span begin="1:33.650" end="1:33.860">め</span><span begin="1:33.860" end="1:34.050">な</span><span begin="1:34.190" end="1:34.300">ル</span><span begin="1:34.300" end="1:34.550">シ</span><span begin="1:34.550" end="1:34.690">ア</span><span begin="1:34.690" end="1:34.740">ン</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甜度适中的俄罗斯鸡尾酒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A lightly sweetened Russian</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Amasa no hikaeme na rushian</span></p><p begin="1:34.990" end="1:37.600" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.990" end="1:35.390">静</span><span begin="1:35.390" end="1:35.640">か</span><span begin="1:35.640" end="1:35.810">な</span><span begin="1:36.110" end="1:36.480">温</span><span begin="1:36.480" end="1:36.690">度</span><span begin="1:36.690" end="1:36.860">が</span><span begin="1:37.040" end="1:37.430">包</span><span begin="1:37.430" end="1:37.600">む</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被静谧的温度包围</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A quiet temperature envelops us</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizuka na ondo ga tsutsumu</span></p><p begin="1:37.890" end="1:42.200" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.890" end="1:38.240">愛</span><span begin="1:38.240" end="1:38.450">し</span><span begin="1:38.450" end="1:38.610">い</span><span begin="1:38.970" end="1:39.350">想</span><span begin="1:39.350" end="1:39.560">い</span><span begin="1:39.560" end="1:39.760">は</span><span begin="1:40.050" end="1:40.400">溶</span><span begin="1:40.400" end="1:41.140">け</span><span begin="1:41.140" end="1:41.810">合</span><span begin="1:41.810" end="1:42.200">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱恋的思绪相互交融</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Beloved feelings melt together</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanashii omoi wa tokeau</span></p><p begin="1:42.520" end="1:47.920" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.520" end="1:43.610">味</span><span begin="1:43.610" end="1:43.900">気</span><span begin="1:44.000" end="1:44.310">な</span><span begin="1:44.310" end="1:44.540">い</span><span begin="1:44.540" end="1:44.890">日</span><span begin="1:44.890" end="1:45.070">々</span><span begin="1:45.070" end="1:45.380">も</span><span begin="1:45.380" end="1:45.780">二</span><span begin="1:45.780" end="1:45.980">人</span><span begin="1:45.980" end="1:46.110">で</span><span begin="1:46.110" end="1:46.460">寄</span><span begin="1:46.460" end="1:46.780">り</span><span begin="1:46.780" end="1:47.180">添</span><span begin="1:47.180" end="1:47.460">え</span><span begin="1:47.460" end="1:47.920">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使是乏味的日子 只要两人相依相偎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even dull days if we stay close together</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ajikenai hibi mo futari de yorisoeba</span></p><p begin="1:48.260" end="1:51.280" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.260" end="1:48.460">き</span><span begin="1:48.460" end="1:48.620">っ</span><span begin="1:48.620" end="1:48.860">と</span><span begin="1:49.280" end="1:49.700">心</span><span begin="1:49.700" end="1:50.070">配</span><span begin="1:50.070" end="1:50.280">は</span><span begin="1:50.280" end="1:50.430">要</span><span begin="1:50.430" end="1:50.760">ら</span><span begin="1:50.760" end="1:50.970">な</span><span begin="1:50.970" end="1:51.280">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一定就无需担心</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Surely there is no need to worry</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kitto shinpai wa iranai</span></p><p begin="1:51.810" end="1:54.210" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.810" end="1:52.070">こ</span><span begin="1:52.070" end="1:52.190">の</span><span begin="1:52.190" end="1:52.370">部</span><span begin="1:52.370" end="1:52.570">屋</span><span begin="1:52.570" end="1:52.770">に</span><span begin="1:52.770" end="1:53.620">帰</span><span begin="1:53.620" end="1:53.880">れ</span><span begin="1:53.880" end="1:54.210">ば</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要回到这个房间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If we return to this room</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono heya ni kaereba</span></p><p begin="1:54.660" end="2:00.290" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.660" end="1:55.400">堅</span><span begin="1:55.400" end="1:55.940">苦</span><span begin="1:55.940" end="1:56.290">し</span><span begin="1:56.290" end="1:56.490">く</span><span begin="1:56.490" end="1:56.720">て</span><span begin="1:56.860" end="1:57.190">息</span><span begin="1:57.190" end="1:57.380">が</span><span begin="1:57.380" end="1:57.550">詰</span><span begin="1:57.550" end="1:57.920">ま</span><span begin="1:57.920" end="1:58.290">る</span><span begin="1:58.290" end="1:58.640">よ</span><span begin="1:58.640" end="1:58.860">う</span><span begin="1:58.860" end="1:59.340">な</span><span begin="1:59.700" end="2:00.290">街</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">令人感到拘谨而窒息的城市</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The stiff and suffocating city</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Katakurushikute iki ga tsumaru you na machi</span></p><p begin="2:00.730" end="2:02.800" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.730" end="2:01.020">真</span><span begin="2:01.120" end="2:01.480">空</span><span begin="2:01.480" end="2:01.700">の</span><span begin="2:01.700" end="2:02.180">暗</span><span begin="2:02.180" end="2:02.800">闇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真空的黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The vacuum of darkness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinkuu no kurayami</span></p><p begin="2:03.270" end="2:06.850" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.270" end="2:03.640">今</span><span begin="2:03.640" end="2:03.800">は</span><span begin="2:03.800" end="2:04.210">遥</span><span begin="2:04.210" end="2:04.580">か</span><span begin="2:04.580" end="2:04.930">遠</span><span begin="2:05.030" end="2:05.300">く</span><span begin="2:05.300" end="2:05.780">に</span><span begin="2:05.780" end="2:06.110">居</span><span begin="2:06.110" end="2:06.850">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻都在遥远的彼方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Are far away right now</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima wa haruka tooku ni iru</span></p><p begin="2:17.880" end="2:20.230" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.880" end="2:18.560">水</span><span begin="2:18.560" end="2:19.670">中</span><span begin="2:19.670" end="2:20.230">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛在水中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Inside the water</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suichuu ni</span></p><p begin="2:20.720" end="2:23.200" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.720" end="2:21.460">沈</span><span begin="2:21.460" end="2:21.770">む</span><span begin="2:21.770" end="2:22.180">よ</span><span begin="2:22.180" end="2:22.590">う</span><span begin="2:22.590" end="2:23.200">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">缓缓下沉般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if sinking</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shizumu you ni</span></p><p begin="2:23.640" end="2:29.070" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.640" end="2:24.280">輪</span><span begin="2:24.280" end="2:25.360">郭</span><span begin="2:25.460" end="2:25.780">が</span><span begin="2:26.160" end="2:26.840">ぼ</span><span begin="2:26.840" end="2:27.340">や</span><span begin="2:27.500" end="2:27.710">け</span><span begin="2:27.820" end="2:28.150">て</span><span begin="2:28.150" end="2:28.450">消</span><span begin="2:28.450" end="2:28.630">え</span><span begin="2:28.630" end="2:28.890">て</span><span begin="2:28.890" end="2:29.070">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">轮廓变得模糊直至消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The outlines blur and fade away</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rinkaku ga boyakete kieteku</span></p><p begin="2:29.330" end="2:34.650" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.330" end="2:29.970">歌</span><span begin="2:29.970" end="2:31.160">声</span><span begin="2:31.160" end="2:31.550">は</span><span begin="2:32.210" end="2:32.890">泡</span><span begin="2:32.890" end="2:33.160">に</span><span begin="2:33.160" end="2:34.000">変</span><span begin="2:34.000" end="2:34.370">わ</span><span begin="2:34.370" end="2:34.650">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">歌声化作了泡沫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The singing voice turns into bubbles</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Utagoe wa awa ni kawaru</span></p><p begin="2:35.040" end="2:39.360" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.040" end="2:35.700">月</span><span begin="2:35.700" end="2:35.950">に</span><span begin="2:36.050" end="2:36.860">照</span><span begin="2:36.860" end="2:37.440">ら</span><span begin="2:37.550" end="2:38.290">さ</span><span begin="2:38.290" end="2:38.820">れ</span><span begin="2:38.990" end="2:39.360">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">沐浴在月光之下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Illuminated by the moon</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuki ni terasarete</span></p><p begin="2:41.110" end="2:43.860" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.110" end="2:41.480">少</span><span begin="2:41.480" end="2:41.710">し</span><span begin="2:41.710" end="2:41.840">く</span><span begin="2:41.840" end="2:42.200">す</span><span begin="2:42.200" end="2:42.420">ぐ</span><span begin="2:42.420" end="2:42.560">っ</span><span begin="2:42.560" end="2:42.910">た</span><span begin="2:42.910" end="2:43.130">い</span><span begin="2:43.130" end="2:43.520">よ</span><span begin="2:43.520" end="2:43.660">う</span><span begin="2:43.660" end="2:43.860">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛有些发痒般</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Feeling slightly ticklish</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukoshi kusuguttai you na</span></p><p begin="2:43.980" end="2:46.480" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.980" end="2:44.330">眠</span><span begin="2:44.330" end="2:44.530">気</span><span begin="2:44.530" end="2:44.650">に</span><span begin="2:44.650" end="2:45.400">誘</span><span begin="2:45.400" end="2:45.710">わ</span><span begin="2:45.710" end="2:46.010">れ</span><span begin="2:46.010" end="2:46.480">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">睡意逐渐袭来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Invited by sleepiness</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemuke ni sasowarete</span></p><p begin="2:46.840" end="2:49.900" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.840" end="2:47.220">ま</span><span begin="2:47.220" end="2:47.430">だ</span><span begin="2:47.890" end="2:48.110">点</span><span begin="2:48.110" end="2:48.280">い</span><span begin="2:48.280" end="2:48.490">て</span><span begin="2:48.490" end="2:48.630">る</span><span begin="2:48.630" end="2:48.980">蛍</span><span begin="2:48.980" end="2:49.330">光</span><span begin="2:49.330" end="2:49.900">灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">依然亮着的荧光灯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The fluorescent light still turned on</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mada tsuiteru keikoutou</span></p><p begin="2:50.370" end="2:52.780" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:50.370" end="2:50.630">フィ</span><span begin="2:50.630" end="2:50.770">ル</span><span begin="2:50.770" end="2:50.960">ム</span><span begin="2:50.960" end="2:51.090">の</span><span begin="2:51.090" end="2:51.730">白</span><span begin="2:51.730" end="2:52.080">に</span><span begin="2:52.180" end="2:52.440">な</span><span begin="2:52.440" end="2:52.780">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">化作胶片上的留白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Turns into the white of the film</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Firumu no shiro ni naru</span></p><p begin="2:53.230" end="2:57.940" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.230" end="2:54.310">氷</span><span begin="2:54.310" end="2:54.540">を</span><span begin="2:54.540" end="2:55.070">口</span><span begin="2:55.070" end="2:55.410">で</span><span begin="2:55.410" end="2:55.770">砕</span><span begin="2:55.770" end="2:55.960">い</span><span begin="2:55.960" end="2:56.100">て</span><span begin="2:56.100" end="2:56.450">キ</span><span begin="2:56.450" end="2:56.830">ス</span><span begin="2:56.830" end="2:57.160">を</span><span begin="2:57.160" end="2:57.440">す</span><span begin="2:57.440" end="2:57.940">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在口中咬碎冰块然后亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crushing ice in the mouth and kissing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koori o kuchi de kudaite kisu o suru</span></p><p begin="2:58.250" end="3:01.360" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.250" end="2:58.620">あ</span><span begin="2:58.620" end="2:58.870">あ</span><span begin="2:59.310" end="2:59.700">冷</span><span begin="2:59.700" end="2:59.900">た</span><span begin="2:59.900" end="3:00.070">い</span><span begin="3:00.070" end="3:00.410">息</span><span begin="3:00.410" end="3:00.720">を</span><span begin="3:00.720" end="3:01.020">吐</span><span begin="3:01.020" end="3:01.360">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊 呼出冰冷的气息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah breathing out a cold breath</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa tsumetai iki o haku</span></p><p begin="3:01.820" end="3:06.130" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:01.820" end="3:02.210">二</span><span begin="3:02.210" end="3:02.410">人</span><span begin="3:02.410" end="3:02.590">は</span><span begin="3:02.590" end="3:02.780">も</span><span begin="3:02.780" end="3:03.160">う</span><span begin="3:03.160" end="3:03.860">夢</span><span begin="3:03.860" end="3:04.350">の</span><span begin="3:04.350" end="3:06.130">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">两人已然身处梦中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The two of us are already inside a dream</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futari wa mou yume no naka</span></p></div></body></tt>